text:
Hello guys! :wave: :wave:
Did you ever had a specific problem with GA4 that was not collecting the session data only on specific subpages under your domain in HubSpot?
I have the same GTM setup everywhere and all the blog posts are sharing the same template and on some of the blog posts GA4 shows 0 sessions in table data view while sessions/page views are seen in HubSpot (and in graph view also visible in GA4). It happens also on some other subpages but they also have the same <header> tag as the rest.
Any reason that could cause this?
